          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-27 10:20:52" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(derivative of {L:κτίζω&lt;SDBG:κτίζω:000000&gt;} ‘to create,’ {D:42.35}) a human institution or social structure as something which has been created</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>institution</Gloss>
                <Gloss>structure</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is possible that κτίσις in {S:06000201300008} may have the implication of authorized institution. It might even be possible to render κτίσις in such a context as ‘authority’ (compare {L:κτίσις&lt;SDBG:κτίσις:000004&gt;}[e] in {D:37.43}).</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
